<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278790>
    dc:description "PLATE 119. A. Scutum and metathorax + propodeum, lateral view. B. Furrow of metathorax + propodeum, frontal view. C, E. Chelae, holotypes. D. Male genitalia. A–C. Gonatopus pajanensis (from Olmi 1989b). D, E. G. pyrillae (from Olmi 1984). Scale bar 0.29 mm for C, 0.19 mm for D and 0.16 mm for E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278790/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

